metadata.description:
Da Vinci Collection

Tiolo: Anatomical studies

Series: Human Body Studies

Unique Number: 1/20

Bill Gates spent $ 30 million to buy the Leicester code ...

In life (probably) you will never have the opportunity to have for
hand one of the manuscripts of the great Leonardo Da Vinci ...

But in Blockchain things are a little different ...

In fact today you can grab the (fine) rights of Leonardo Da Vinci's works, and being the first to do it, with a little imagination, you can make your friends believe that the manuscripts are your work!

And then you never know, maybe sooner or later someone forgets about this thing and tea becomes a genius for everyone ...

And all for little more than a $ !!!

The collection consists of 8 series: human body studies, drafts and drawings of human portraits, studies and drawings of animals, studies and drawings of battles, studies of details for paintings, drawings of panoramas and various subjects, drawings and designs of machines and attack and defense systems, studies and sketches for monuments and villas.

All tokens are unique and will have only one owner!

The series will be released one at a time, and the next series will come out when the previous one has at least 75% of the manuscripts ...

In the end, if the 8 series are sold, the Master Manuscripts will be released, which will be the highlight of the collection ...
